{"tid":1128818,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"湯家驊：移交逃犯無關對方人權法治狀況　稱沒說服力民意不具代表性","createTime":"2019-04-28T05:42:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-28T11:58:15.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"75673fdc5b709b12540672e3a6af6b40c0643908","tid":1128818,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T05:42:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180927/large/1538028614_d270.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180927%2Flarge%2F1538028614_d270.jpg&h=08899f46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n民間人權陣線今午4時舉行反對修訂《逃犯條例》遊行，行政會議成員、資深大律師湯家驊早上出席無綫節目「講清講楚」時，被問及若遊行人數較預期為多，政府是否需要讓步以促成《逃犯條例》通過，湯家驊稱若特首林鄭月娥問他意見，他認為是不值得讓步。<br />\n<br />\n湯家驊表示，現時反對修訂《逃犯條例》的聲音都是政治口號，「都是不理解移交疑犯是什麽東西，所提出的憂慮都是法例已經有保障，沒說服力的民意是不具代表性的」。<br />\n<br />\n湯家驊續說，他已督促港府開展修例20多年，若港府因誤解聲音而投降，未來將很難作有效管治。<br />\n<br />\n另外，湯家驊強調移交逃犯與對方法治或人權狀況無關，重點在於香港本身司法制度，又稱「就算23條立法，23條罪行也不能放在（《逃犯條例》）裏面，因為它是政治罪行」。"},{"pid":"7f591ccf5fc7771b15655cc35bbd53ad5e468ebe","tid":1128818,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T05:42:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190428/s00001/1556424021823/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190428%2Fs00001%2F1556424021823%2F&d=VPc2G2a59adbLf1ajQMU8miIh%2BLW8fuN5Q3LPFa5L7A%3D&h=63bcc053\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190428%2Fs00001%2F1556424021823%2F&h=11625ba2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190428/s00001/1556424021823/</a>"},{"pid":"81bef9d8bc929fef203a21cd6292cb8a4a096fc6","tid":1128818,"uid":113373,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T05:45:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">湯渣</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" c